{"tid":204516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫北者︰倘受襲 北韓特工潛南韓擄西方人質","createTime":"2017-04-17T06:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T08:24:25.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9e0ee9ce6c1bfd1db4a49d2e4dd83d7d069c5e","tid":204516,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>脫北者︰倘受襲 北韓特工潛南韓擄西方人質<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170416/56570880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170416%2F56570880&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=8c0d37b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170416%2F56570880&h=0ca6e99f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170416/56570880</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170416/large/1492318568_4783.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170416%2Flarge%2F1492318568_4783.jpg&h=597768f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申相玉、金正日及崔銀姬的合照（左起）(互聯網)</div><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮半島戰雲密佈，美國日前調派「卡爾文森號」航空母艦打擊群前赴朝鮮半島水域，加上北韓試射導彈，令外界擔心美國和北韓的戰事一觸即發。有脫北者就指，北韓為防與其他國家發生衝突，早就秘密訓練特工潛入南韓綁架西方遊客做人質。<br />\n<br />\n37歲姓李（Ung-gil Lee）脫北者在北韓秘密單位工作6年，他指北韓一旦遇襲，領導人金正恩的反應將與敍利亞總統巴沙爾（Bashar al-Assad）不同，「他會反擊，採取一切報復措施」。他又指，北韓早就秘密訓練特工到南韓綁架西方遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「最好是將他們綁架再帶到北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，否則會在南韓綁架外國人當人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」；他又補充人質會被撕票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n李曾效力「暴風軍團」，他17歲加入特種部隊，接受1年洗腦教育再接受5年訓練成為通訊員。他指訓練刻苦，要接受極端組織「伊斯蘭國」形式的恐襲訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，包括每天要接受拳擊訓練及在寒冷海中游泳等。<br />\n<br />\n李指北韓會經海路、半空和隧道派員滲透進入南韓，他是被派到南韓破壞基建、擾亂道路港口，以及綁架外國人的100名特工之一，「我們潛入南韓，換衣服，走入許多外國人的地方，再綁架他們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。我們會記住主要大使館的地點、電話號碼和車牌」。<br />\n<br />\n李又指，他們要攜帶可令心臟麻痹的毒藥，讓他們當做武器使用或自殺，「這是自殺任務，我們應該要回去，但如果不能，我們就要自殺」。李最後選擇與妻子和姐妹逃走，2006年到南韓從事理財顧問。<br />\n<br />\n北韓到南韓綁架人質並非鮮見，南韓導演申相玉和影星妻子崔銀姬1978年被綁架到北韓，他們被綁後專職為金正日製作電影和宣傳片。7年後兩人藉參加德國柏林影展，在奧地利首都維也納乘機竄入美國大使館尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日郵報》"},{"pid":"9d696afa7095b98d1b41f3cac895b5be8f532699","tid":204516,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"人質會被撕票仲叫唔叫人質?"},{"pid":"b8e081d3bf69157b12f4736340006f3b3cb2a26b","tid":204516,"uid":4545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"人質會被撕票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f7bbf924f82b79c405aee400ee3fb42ba24e28","tid":204516,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人質會被撕票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬:無有怕"},{"pid":"7eb09cdf4287cc93cbce297153b0dce91977a390","tid":204516,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人質會被撕票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬:無有怕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已請假同報佐團。對旅行社有信心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac88f201bb2c0e29b93c43ff71102596bca78256","tid":204516,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人質會被撕票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比錢都唔要真係無得輸"},{"pid":"2d88fb7e338ef46f69205ab7ae9da428d1cee049","tid":204516,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}